WEBVTT

00:13:27.112 --> 00:13:30.378
He tells him how to say a noble goodbye,

00:13:30.378 --> 00:13:34.225
a goodbye that's fit for a hero.

00:13:34.225 --> 00:13:36.974
"As if long-prepared,

00:13:36.974 --> 00:13:39.653
as if courageous,

00:13:39.653 --> 00:13:42.250
as it becomes you

00:13:42.250 --> 00:13:44.422
who were worthy of such a city,

00:13:44.422 --> 00:13:46.825
approach the window with a firm step,

00:13:46.825 --> 00:13:49.360
and with emotion,

00:13:49.360 --> 00:13:51.559
but not with the entreaties

00:13:51.559 --> 00:13:54.320
or the complaints of a coward,

00:13:54.320 --> 00:13:56.291
as a last enjoyment,

00:13:56.291 --> 00:13:58.415
listen to the sounds,

00:13:58.415 --> 00:14:01.749
the exquisite instruments of the musical troops,